result.name: senior-staff-expenses
result.notes: These datasets show the expense claims of HEFCE senior staff – these are staff at director-level and above. Monthly summary data for individuals is provided under categories of spend such as rail, taxis, hotels. Our travel and subsistence policy sets out the rules and allowances which apply when travelling on HEFCE business.

organization.name: higher-education-funding-council-for-england
organization.title: Higher Education Funding Council for England
organization.description: HEFCE distributes public money for higher education to universities and colleges in England, and ensures that this money is used to deliver the greatest benefit to students and the wider public.
